metadata.description:
Clarity is a consequence,
of surrendering to a higher will.
Faith is the prerequisite for moving forward,
trusting, above all, in yourself.

In the very will of your heart,
that allows you to navigate the waters.
When they become dark,
and the present is flooded with tireless time.

With a doubt that lurks,
bringing with it the valuable information.
That if you hesitate it is because you care,
you just have to learn to read.

What is hidden between the lines,
like the engine that will allow you to move forward.
Following that invisible force,
that illuminates the path of your dreams.

Santiago, 27 December 2022
